
### Регистрация работника магазина (staff)
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Password: admin1

{
  "storeId": 1,
  "login": "store_1_staff",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Регистрация менеджера магазина
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Password: admin1

{
  "storeId": 1,
  "login": "store_1_manager",
  "password": "manager123",
  "role": "manager"
}

